title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 - Sep 01 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 - Sep 01 2022
description:
The CIA has become the Detroit Lions of federal agencies. Clinton lackey, John Brennan: It’s clear that Trump has "nefarious intentions" for keeping classified documents. With 9% inflation and $4 gas, Treasurer Secretary Yellen kicks off month-long economic victory tour. The GOP needs to go on offense. The NYC subways are something out of Escape from New York. Buck refuses to give up his plastic bags. Pennsylvania Senate candidate, Dr. Mehmet Oz, joins Clay and Buck to discuss the policies of his socialist opponent, John Fetterman, and how vital these midterm elections are for the country. A legitimate question: Is John Fetterman healthy enough to represent the people of Pennsylvania?

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
